article_id:2434,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1630303200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added featured dragon:</div><div>5★ Gala Beast Volk (wind)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1630303200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1630648799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>
