	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8e762fc1fa1804dc9be5379a14026bd22.png"></span>
				<span>Lunatic Deliverance</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Grants the user the "Blood Moon" effect,<br>grants the entire team a team strength amp,<br>and activates "Skill Shift."<br>This skill will become Lunatic Desolation<br>and be immediately readied for use.<br><br>Lunatic Desolation consumes Blood Moon<br>and all stacks of Moonlit Rage, deals damage<br>to surrounding enemies, and inflicts stun.<br>This attack deals additional damage based on<br>the number of Moonlit Rage stacks consumed.<br>If this skill has become Lunatic Desolation<br>and not yet been used when the user's<br>remaining shapeshift time runs out, it will be<br>used automatically.</div><div class="skill-detail">Special Effects:<br>・Blood Moon<br>　　Does not stack<br>Team Amps:<br>・Team Strength Amp (MAX Lv. = 3)<br><br><color=#00008B>Phase II:</color><br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 0 to 3 Stacks): 1,098 × 1 hit<br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 4 to 6 Stacks): 1,618 × 1 hit<br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 7 to 9 Stacks): 2,244 × 1 hit<br>Damage (Moonlit Rage = 10 Stacks): 3,600 × 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>・Stun<br>　　Lasts 7 seconds</div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/65d6cd12143fa0ae6dd9c9d0d7ecd0b12.png"></span><span>(Wind) Fangs of the Fangless V</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>increases strength by 100%.<br><br>Also, regardless of their attunement, grants<br>the user a dragon strike while shapeshifted<br>as Beast Volk. This dragon strike deals<br>damage to enemies in a line and reduces<br>their defense by 10% for five seconds.<br>This defense reduction will not stack.<br><br>While charging this dragon strike, the user will<br>be granted a stack of the "Moonlit Rage" effect<br>at set intervals. Moonlit Rage can stack up to<br>ten times.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5d704441d2fe504b34ded414abd9ef9b2.png"></span><span>(Wind) Plague of Weakness II</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>increases the chances of inflicting any<br>afflictions by 100%, the duration of poison<br>and stormlash inflicted on enemies by 30%,<br>damage to poisoned enemies by 15%, and<br>damage to stormlashed enemies by 15%.<br><br>Also, regardless of their attunement, lowers<br>the user's affliction resistance by 150%, but<br>activates the following effects every 3.5 seconds<br>while they have the "Blood Moon" effect:<br>・The user is granted a stack of the "Moonlit<br>Rage" effect.<br>・Damage is dealt to surrounding enemies,<br>and 10% of the damage inflicted is restored<br>as HP to the entire team. This recovery caps<br>at 10% of each adventurer's maximum HP.<br>The effect of the Dragon's Fierce Rule ability<br>will not apply to this damage.<br><br>When the user's shapeshift is undone, they<br>will be inflicted with poison for 12 seconds,<br>their dragon skill's "Skill Shift" will be reset,<br>and the Blood Moon effect and all stacks of<br>Moonlit Rage will be lost.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Some dragons will allow you to use a special ability called dragon strike when you shapeshift. For further information, please see the in-game Help section.</div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Gala Beast Volk&#39;s Attacks<br>While shapeshifted into Gala Beast Volk, the third attack of a standard combo will deal damage to enemies directly ahead and inflict stormlash.</div><div><br></div><div>Note: For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1630216800,update_time1629948849